item.title: About Us
item.dc:creator: user
item.content:encoded: Ukrop’s is the brand you’ve come to trust for consistent quality and great taste. Now, with pick-up and delivery available, we are making it easy for you to impress your guests with table-ready, fresh and flavorful foods. Our White House Roll® sandwiches with Cheddar Pimento Cheese, Smithfield Ham, or Classic Chicken Salad, are perfect for any occasion. Featuring Mrs. Marshall’s Potato Salad and Cole Slaw, we offer a variety of Richmond’s favorite foods. Our signature Chocolate Fudge, Lemon Chess, and Southern Pecan Tarts with whipped topping are must-have desserts and the delicious finish to any meal. And, since an important component of catering is presentation – we’ve got you covered with attractive platters and bowls that will make your job hassle-free and your event elegant! Whether you want to treat your best clients or ensure your family function is memorable, we hope you will trust Catering by Ukrop’s to make your meal planning easy.   Call 804-340-3020 or email orders@cateringbyukrops.com to place your order today!

wp:postmeta.wp:meta_value: Impress your guests with fresh and flavorful foods
Ukrop’s Catering makes your job hassle-free and your event elegant, whether you’re looking to treat your best clients or ensure your family function is memorable.
The bakers at Ukrop’s can create standout cakes for any special occasion.
From simple to elegant, corporate to social, business lunch to special events, we’ve designed a menu that’s sure to please a crowd.
